webwork-tex.statement: The function \[f(s,t,u) = \left(t+u,u+s,s+t\right)\] has \mbox{\parbox[t]{3ex}{\hrulefill}} inputs and \mbox{\parbox[t]{3ex}{\hrulefill}} outputs. Thus it is of the form \[f\colon {\bf R}^n \to {\bf R}^m\] where \(n\) = \mbox{\parbox[t]{3ex}{\hrulefill}} and \(m\) = \mbox{\parbox[t]{3ex}{\hrulefill}}.
